org.artorg.tools.phantomData.server.boot

Interface ConsoleFrame

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FxConsoleFrame

    public interface ConsoleFrame
    A graphical logging pane that shows the command line output.

    Note: If some lines are logged in static initializer they will not be shown in the panel.
